Unitech Falls After Shareholders Reject Payment of Dividend

-- B y   S u r e s h   S e s h a d r i
-- 
2011-09-30T03:47:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/unitech-falls-after-shareholders-reject-payment-of-dividend.html
Unitech Ltd. (UT)  fell in Mumbai trading
after the company said shareholders didn’t approve the payment
of dividend and that the resolution for declaration of dividend
on equity shares for the financial year ended March 31, was
“rescinded.”  The stock declined 1.1 percent to 26.70 rupees as of 9:17
a.m. local time.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Suresh Seshadri at 
 sseshadri1@bloomberg.net  